    net.fortuna.ical4j.model.AbstractContentFactory
    net.fortuna.ical4j.model.CalendarDateFormatFactory
    adoption of the new date/time API means formatting is now supported via DateTimeFormatter
    net.fortuna.ical4j.model.ComponentFactoryImpl
    net.fortuna.ical4j.model.Date
    Use LocalDate for iCalendar DATE representations.
    net.fortuna.ical4j.filter.DateInRangeRule 
    net.fortuna.ical4j.model.DateRange
    We can no longer use DateRange to compare dates reliably due to supporting incompatible temporal types. Use Interval instead.
    net.fortuna.ical4j.util.Dates
    Utility class for old date/time API no longer required
    net.fortuna.ical4j.model.DateTime
    Use Instant, LocalDateTime or ZonedDateTime for iCalendar DATE-TIME representations.
    net.fortuna.ical4j.model.Dur
    Replaced by TemporalAmount implementations such as Duration and Period in Java 8.
    net.fortuna.ical4j.model.Iso8601
    Replaced with new Java Date/Time API implementation
    net.fortuna.ical4j.model.LocationTypeList
    replaced with standard Java collections.
    net.fortuna.ical4j.model.ParameterFactoryImpl

    net.fortuna.ical4j.model.PropertyFactoryImpl
    net.fortuna.ical4j.model.PropertyFactoryRegistry
    net.fortuna.ical4j.model.Time
    Use LocalTime for iCalendar TIME representations.
    net.fortuna.ical4j.model.UtcOffset
    Replaced by ZoneOffset in Java 8.
